STATE
v.
Jose Ismael-Ruiz ZUNIGA 292P13-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 22, 2016 Joan M. Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Jose Ismael-Ruiz Zuniga, for Zuniga, Jose Ismael.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th of July 2016 by Defendant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd of September 2016."
